# Profit Or Loss Foreign Exchange Gains Amount

## identifier
de13808

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, for any gains on foreign exchange recognised in the profit or loss. This item is determined in accordance with the relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.ForeignExchangeGains.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.19
- period=duration
